    # "(We arrive in the Dwell.)"
    "（住穴に着いた）"

# game/script/demo/script_3_dwell.rpy:21
translate japanese script_3_83f146aa:

    # "{image=sight}(The walls of this mine are covered in a Saturated Thread of some kind.{w} They're all different colors, spun by different hands.)"
    "{image=sight}（坑道の壁は何かしらの満たされた糸で覆われている。{w}さまざまな人の手で紡がれた、さまざまな色の糸だ）"

# game/script/demo/script_3_dwell.rpy:24
translate japanese script_3_d68575e4:

    # "{image=smell}(It smells strange, like citrus and mildew.{w} Something about it makes me feel faint.{w} Am I allergic?)"
    "{image=smell}（妙なにおいがする。柑橘系の香りと白カビのにおい。{w}少しめまいを感じる。{w}アレルギーなのかな？）"

# game/script/demo/script_3_dwell.rpy:27
translate japanese script_3_4deb5b1c:

    # "{image=hearing}(For a mine, they sure aren't mining very heavily.{w} Probably because it's a day off...?)"
    "{image=hearing}（坑道なのに、採掘作業の音は聞こえない。{w}今日はお休み？）"

# game/script/demo/script_3_dwell.rpy:41
translate japanese script_3_1d860011:

    # "(We walk for a while, passing many rooms...)"
    "（わたしたちはしばらく歩いた。たくさんの部屋がある…）"

# game/script/demo/script_3_dwell.rpy:42
translate japanese script_3_9b17cc6c:

    # "(Without Amour and Betz guiding me, I'm not sure I would be able to find my way around.)"
